Package net.rtccloud.sdk.exception

Package that defines custom Exceptions used in the SDK

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    RtccIllegalArgumentException
    Mimics the IllegalArgumentException.
    RtccIllegalStateException
    Mimics the IllegalStateException.
    RtccPermissionRequiredException
    This exception is thrown by the RtccEngine at Rtcc.initialize(String, android.content.Context) when the requested Manifest.permissions can not be found in the AndroidManifest.xml file
    RtccRuntimeException
    The RuntimeException used by Rtcc SDK
    RtccUnsupportedOperationException
    Mimics the UnsupportedOperationException.
